title: Lubnnan
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Beer/Wine, Delivery, Take-out, Arabic, Lebanese, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Family-owned and operated. Serves traditional Arabic food with plenty of vegan options including falafel, tabouleh, spinach and zaatar sfihas, pita bread, hummus, babaganoush, fried aubergines, mjadra and more. Has 2 large spaces and lots of tables so reservations are not necessary unless you are in a big group.
